reviewText: Won't play in my DVD player. I guess this is region specific. Seller did not specify in his description

If you're a fan of the FLC then this will make you VERY happy!
Filmed live at their concert in London at Shepherds Bush Empire.
26 songs! Over 2 hours of footage including the 4 FLC news webisode's featuring me, Wayne Lazar!
Buy it NOW, you won't be sorry for long!
